cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "rat_pipeline: RNA-only somatic-like variant detection"
abstract: >-
  Pipeline for detecting somatic-like / treatment-enriched non-germline
  variants from RNA-seq alone (no matched DNA), using observation-first
  differential calling with imputation-as-filter. Developed and validated
  on the rat PHMG_IT dataset (rn7) against WGS DNA ground truth.
type: software
authors:
